      <p class="post__essential__desc">
        Athletes and non-athletes enjoy it equally · no fitness required to step into the canoe.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="post__essential">
      <span class="post__essential__icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 18V5l12-2v13"/><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"/><circle cx="18" cy="16" r="3"/></svg>
      </span>
      <h3 class="post__essential__label">Built-in atmosphere</h3>
      <p class="post__essential__desc">
